lead_paragraph: J.J. Watt is out until at least December and could miss the rest of the season with an injured back, leaving the Texans searching for ways to deal with the loss of the NFL's best defensive player.

headline.print_headline: Texans Place Star DE JJ Watt on Injured Reserve
